        <page n="01" image="va.au.rv.1863.09.18.01">
            <pageNote>This page contains a list of deserters from the 52nd Regiment of Virginia
                Volunteers, the text of a speech by Governor Letcher before a special meeting of the
                General Assembly, and advertisements.</pageNote>
